alaxy mass build-up process and\nlimiting the stellar mass growth, in a ``maintenance mode\" feedback.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Tue, 21 Mar 2023 17:19:39 GMT"}],"update_date":"2023-03-22"}
