nce regularity of the solutions to any desired degree?\nIn order to answer these questions, we study the corresponding characteristic\ninitial value problem. In particular, we investigate in detail the appearance\nof singularities at expansion orders $n=0,\\dots,4$ for angular modes\n$\\ell=0,\\dots,4$.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Tue, 21 Mar 2023 20:48:20 GMT"}],"update_date":"2023-03-23"}
