ards very\nlow galaxy stellar masses the trend observed at high masses. Finally, by\ncombining our model with the MIST isochrone database, we compare our synthetic\ncolour-magnitude diagrams to observations.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Wed, 22 Mar 2023 13:04:39 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Tue, 2 May 2023 11:00:18 GMT"}],"update_date":"2023-05-10"}
