9\nms/keV, which may correspond to different origins of the bursts. These spectral\nlag features may have important implications on the magnetar bursts.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Wed, 22 Mar 2023 13:18:23 GMT"}],"update_date":"2023-03-29"}
